item.title: Thanks for making RackerHacker so popular!
item.description: After a quick review of the stats this evening, I found that this blog has made it to 500,000 sessions so far this year. Page views are just past 2.5 million! In 2007, there were over 65,000 sessions and over 427,000 million page views in 2007 as a final count. Here’s the exact numbers as of tonight: 2008 Year to Date: Sessions: 501,166 Pageviews: 2,506,011 Hits: 7,414,333 Bytes Transferred: 65.
